        "2": {
            "title": "The Ruins of Ashur",
            "story_hook": "Leaving the desert sun behind, Amara and Tariq descend into the cool depths of the canyon cave. The tunnel opens into a vast subterranean city—the ancient Ashur. But bandits have turned the ruins into their camp, and the stones themselves are beginning to stir with ancient magic.",
            "completion_summary": "With the Stone Emperor defeated, the heart of Ashur is safe. As Amara and Tariq stand among the ancient ruins, they realize this is just the beginning. Inspired by their adventures together, they make a pact: to explore the world beyond these lands, to see what wonders await, and to face whatever challenges come their way—together.",
