        "3": {
            "title": "The Misty Foothills",
            "story_hook": "The biting air of the Jade Peaks greeted Amara and Tariq as they arrived in the high mountains. Shrouded in mist, a young boy named Kenji sat on a rock, clutching an oversized wooden sword. His eyes widened with excitement and surprise at their arrival. 'Who are you?' he asked, before hurriedly explaining how the Shadow Master's forces had begun to invade his mountains, spreading a dark, unnatural mist across the land.",
            "completion_summary": "The Iron Enforcer has been driven back, and the mists have momentarily parted. Kenji, impressed by the newcomers' bravery and wisdom, wipes his brow and offers a formal bow. The path to the peaks is dangerous, but with new allies, the journey upward has just begun.",
            "mystery_path": "The trail leads higher into the frozen heights...",
